30:46.734 --> 30:48.380
I really have to go.

30:50.770 --> 30:51.802
Bye, Grace.

30:56.901 --> 30:59.610
Bye. Call me.

31:05.830 --> 31:07.913
I looked for you at lunch.

31:08.426 --> 31:09.702
Do I know you?

31:09.822 --> 31:11.955
