31:14.213 --> 31:15.884
Hi, Kathy's boyfriend.

31:16.084 --> 31:16.872
What can I do for you?

31:16.891 --> 31:19.206
You can stop pretending
you need a spelling partner.

31:19.326 --> 31:21.214
If you want some help, I'll help you.

31:21.239 --> 31:22.825
(Laughs)

31:22.945 --> 31:24.424
What's your GPA?

31:24.724 --> 31:26.876
