31:27.283 --> 31:28.760
Little joke.

31:29.066 --> 31:31.012
Doesn't matter what grades I make,

31:31.132 --> 31:33.633
I'm smarter than you, and
I'm better looking than you,

31:33.753 --> 31:35.754
and Kathy likes me more than you.

31:35.786 --> 31:37.375
We're just friends.

31:37.694 --> 31:40.377
And I do need the help getting
ready for State. You can spell?

31:40.497 --> 31:42.586
- Throw me one.
- Ubiquitous.

31:42.642 --> 31:44.737
Please. (Laughs)

31:44.794 --> 31:47.772
U-b-i-q-u-i-t-o-u-s.

31:47.784 --> 31:49.123
Give me something a
little more challenging.

31:49.186 --> 31:50.312
Coquettishly.

31:50.343 --> 31:53.484
C-o-q-u-e-t-t-i-s-h-l-y.

31:53.484 --> 31:55.117
Opprobrious.

31:56.274 --> 31:58.645
- A-p-
- (Buzzes) Wrong!

32:04.784 --> 32:07.505
Geez, the girl troubles
just won't go away, huh?

32:07.518 --> 32:09.876
- No girl trouble.
- You're in trouble with me.

32:09.996 --> 32:12.172
- You said I was cheating.
- How smart are you?

32:12.292 --> 32:14.912
You copied my paper, every single answer.

32:15.032 --> 32:18.329
If you'd changed even one of
your answers, you'd be home-free.

32:18.449 --> 32:21.075
And I didn't exactly say
you were cheating, I just

32:21.094 --> 32:22.658
said I wasn't covering my paper.

32:22.696 --> 32:24.366
- I hate algebra.
- Well.

32:24.397 --> 32:25.824
I do too, but

32:25.944 --> 32:27.613
apparently, I'm getting better at it,

32:27.733 --> 32:28.902
if you want some help...

32:28.958 --> 32:31.748
Really? You have time
to help me and have a...

32:32.267 --> 32:33.744
What were you doing when I walked up?

32:33.732 --> 32:35.446
Having some sort of spell off?

32:35.452 --> 32:37.774
Believe me, I'd rather punch the guy

32:37.894 --> 32:40.721
but that would be too easy and
I'd get kicked out of school

32:41.009 --> 32:41.885
and then I'd never get,

32:42.005 --> 32:44.025
you know, anywhere with Kathy.

32:44.081 --> 32:46.427
Yeah, I know.

32:46.615 --> 32:47.816
Just do me a favor,

32:48.091 --> 32:49.856
don't text me any offers.

32:49.906 --> 32:52.639
I've had some problems in that area.

32:52.759 --> 32:53.772
So have I.

32:54.078 --> 32:54.923
Really?

32:55.105 --> 32:56.018
Yeah.

32:56.637 --> 32:58.164
I'm sure neither of us

32:58.284 --> 33:00.517
wants to make the same mistake twice.

33:00.567 --> 33:02.224
I'm sure.

33:02.281 --> 33:03.788
Are you?

33:06.072 --> 33:08.443
Never had that happen before.

33:09.500 --> 33:11.765
How did the condom break?

33:12.580 --> 33:14.169
Uh. I don't know.

33:14.289 --> 33:16.471
Well, it's your fault, you were wearing it.

33:16.797 --> 33:18.999
Okay, but uh...

33:19.018 --> 33:20.138
you're on the pill, right?

33:20.338 --> 33:21.195
Yes.

33:21.264 --> 33:23.066
Weren't you on the pill when
you got pregnant with Ben?

33:23.186 --> 33:24.579
I was changing pills,

33:24.617 --> 33:26.594
