kind of pill and another

33:26.600 --> 33:28.152
and I don't want to talk about it.

33:28.928 --> 33:29.978
All right.

33:31.142 --> 33:33.588
Well. If you're worried about it, you could

33:33.708 --> 33:35.446
get a morning-after pill, couldn't you?

33:36.235 --> 33:38.643
Yeah. Yeah. I guess.

33:38.687 --> 33:41.621
But I'm not that worried about it.

33:41.921 --> 33:42.860
Right.

33:42.928 --> 33:44.404
What's the worst that can happen?

33:45.531 --> 33:48.008
I get pregnant and then
you get what you want,

33:48.128 --> 33:50.918
I'd have to go with you to New York.

33:54.534 --> 33:56.229
But you are on the pill?

33:56.236 --> 33:57.574
Yeah, yeah.

33:57.694 --> 33:59.107
