called me or texted me.

34:50.110 --> 34:51.775
I could have. You're right. I'm sorry.

34:51.895 --> 34:53.452
I've got another surprise for you.

34:53.521 --> 34:54.710
- Really?
- Really.

34:54.710 --> 34:56.112
Are you giving me the money for school?

34:56.175 --> 34:57.945
What? No. That's not the surprise.

34:57.976 --> 34:58.852
