35:01.042 --> 35:03.575
Oh, dear lord. Amy!

35:03.600 --> 35:04.795
You're all grown up.

35:05.120 --> 35:06.609
- Uh...
- I'll give you a hint.

35:06.803 --> 35:08.305
She's my mother.

35:08.367 --> 35:10.726
Oh Amy, you turned out... nice.

35:10.763 --> 35:11.933
Grandma?

35:12.253 --> 35:15.650
What! I thought you were
living in a biosphere in Sweden.

35:15.650 --> 35:17.371
I was. For a while.

35:17.433 --> 35:19.767
Too confining though, had to hit the road.

35:19.942 --> 35:21.169
How have you been?

35:21.344 --> 35:22.683
Uh...

35:22.803 --> 35:23.778
She knows.

35:23.790 --> 35:26.562
Can't wait to meet Ricky
and my great grandson.

35:26.606 --> 35:28.439
I love saying that.

35:28.996 --> 35:31.605
Can you believe I'm a great grandmother?

35:31.905 --> 35:33.919
Hell, I look so young,

35:33.938 --> 35:35.277
a couple of people have

35:35.277 --> 35:36.891
mistaken me for his wife today.

35:36.935 --> 35:38.280
Oh.

35:38.400 --> 35:39.443
Nice.

35:40.626 --> 35:42.303
It's so good to see you, grandma.

35:42.423 --> 35:45.756
I think. Are you sticking around?

35:45.813 --> 35:47.088
I'm sticking around for tonight.

35:47.282 --> 35:49.166
Tonight? What's tonight?

35:53.545 --> 35:56.185
