36:20.848 --> 36:22.325
and have no other friends.

36:22.381 --> 36:24.546
You have girlfriends, hang out with them,

36:24.615 --> 36:26.730
maybe Jody or Francine
need help with spelling.

36:26.748 --> 36:28.206
No, they don't.

36:28.782 --> 36:31.979
Why couldn't you have just been nice
to Brian so we could all be friends?

36:32.022 --> 36:32.980
We need friends,

36:32.968 --> 36:35.089
we don't need to just
hang out with each other.

36:35.132 --> 36:36.146
Why not?

36:36.619 --> 36:38.655
You're afraid you'll
want to have sex with me?

36:38.837 --> 36:40.545
I'm not having sex in high school again.

36:40.607 --> 36:42.596
So if you want to have sex,

36:42.584 --> 36:43.422
then have sex with Layla,

36:43.435 --> 36:45.412
because it's not going to be me.

36:46.575 --> 36:48.896
- Okay. I take that back.
- Too late.

36:49.510 --> 36:51.949
We could maybe make-out a little.

36:58.550 --> 37:00.521
You sure you don't want to
get that morning after pill?

37:00.540 --> 37:01.859
I'm sure.

37:02.798 --> 37:04.875
All right, well,

37:05.294 --> 37:06.952
I hate that I have to leave again.

37:07.189 --> 37:09.129
That's all right, you'll be back.

37:09.486 --> 37:11.400
Yes, I will.

37:15.060 --> 37:16.919
- I guess you're right.
- About what?

37:16.981 --> 37:19.071
