me into getting married

38:28.030 --> 38:29.707
and into moving to New York,

38:30.026 --> 38:31.590
I am not going to be pressured.

38:31.710 --> 38:34.374
Wasn't doing that. Just talking.

38:37.227 --> 38:39.022
A year from June.

38:42.676 --> 38:44.934
I want to finish my sophomore year

38:45.435 --> 38:49.089
and then I'll transfer
to somewhere in New York.

38:49.352 --> 38:50.684
I'll take it.

38:54.219 --> 38:55.977
You wanna put that ring back on?

39:05.487 --> 39:06.726
Thanks for hanging out with me.

39:07.120 --> 39:08.803
Almost closing time.

39:09.297 --> 39:11.168
- Yep.
- You okay?

39:11.231 --> 39:12.795
Yeah Leo, I'm good.

39:13.301 --> 39:15.691
Of course we haven't talked
about the one thing I thought

39:15.716 --> 39:17.837
you wanted me to come
down here and talk about.

39:17.957 --> 39:19.940
Couldn't decide if I wanted to bring it up.

39:20.178 --> 39:21.804
She's going to marry Ricky, right?

39:21.810 --> 39:22.486
I think so.

39:22.493 --> 39:23.963
And then she's going to
go off to summer school

39:23.982 --> 39:25.396
in New York with Ben.

39:25.777 --> 39:27.366
- She didn't tell you?
- No.

39:27.410 --> 39:28.743
Then don't say anything,

39:28.863 --> 39:31.039
maybe she hasn't even Ben told me.

39:31.159 --> 39:32.143
Told Ricky.

39:32.153 --> 39:35.187
Summer school starts the
week after high school's over.

39:35.738 --> 39:37.608
And Amy wants to start in summer school.

39:37.671 --> 39:39.369
I knew there was something
she wasn't telling me.

39:39.489 --> 39:41.171
Why on earth would Ricky agree to that?

39:41.205 --> 39:44.127
I don't know. I think he just
desperately wants to marry

39:44.142 --> 39:45.342
the mother of his son.

39:45.376 --> 39:47.091
And I guess that's the only
way she thinks she can go to

39:47.105 --> 39:48.255
New York and not feel guilty.

39:48.280 --> 39:49.268
I got to talk to her.

39:49.244 --> 39:51.384
But not tonight. Tonight's your night.

39:53.284 --> 39:55.986
Okay, daddy, we're ready.

39:58.791 --> 39:59.917
Good luck.

40:00.192 --> 40:02.407
- Congratulations.
- Thanks, Leo.

40:16.022 --> 40:18.141
We are gathered here together tonight

40:18.176 --> 40:20.410
on this happy and joyous occasion

40:20.445 --> 40:22.466
to rejoin these two people

40:23.023 --> 40:24.543
in holy matrimony.

40:26.934 --> 40:28.717
- Are you okay?
- Yes.

40:29.320 --> 40:31.087
We could be next.

40:33.779 --> 40:36.325
Marriage is an awesome institution,

40:36.926 --> 40:39.396
God's way of giving us a lifelong lesson

40:39.430 --> 40:40.899
in forgiveness

40:41.343 --> 40:43.514
and acceptance and love.

40:44.168 --> 40:45.711
It is forgiveness and acceptance

40:45.698 --> 40:47.287
that have brought us here tonight

40:47.632 --> 40:50.748
and love that will keep
this family together.

40:51.275 --> 40:54.411
(Both sobbing)

40:56.347 --> 40:58.381
I felt the same way at my wedding.

40:58.416 --> 41:00.558
Me too. But I did it anyway.

41:00.564 --> 41:03.054
Is everyone okay, should we continue?

41:03.087 --> 41:03.798
Yeah, it's good.

41:03.855 --> 41:05.994
If you two would face one another please?

41:08.359 --> 41:09.316
George,

41:10.136 --> 41:12.958
do you take Kathleen
to be your wedded wife?

41:15.405 --> 41:16.418
I do.

41:18.245 --> 41:19.253
I do.

41:20.717 --> 41:21.805
I do.

41:22.675 --> 41:24.528
- And Kathleen...
- Yes.

41:26.174 --> 41:28.278
Do you take George to
be your wedded husband?

41:28.314 --> 41:29.312
I do.

41:29.347 --> 41:30.347
(Sobbing)

41:48.621 --> 41:49.966
Mom?

41:50.836 --> 41:52.168
Are you up?

41:54.338 --> 41:55.338
Mom?

41:57.241 --> 41:59.209
Do you want some breakfast?

42:02.280 --> 42:03.280
Mom?

